Landing.HeroSubHeading.SubHeadingHero: Ukwakha, ukulinganisa, nokuhlalutya imodeli, iindlela, kunye neendlela ezinamandla. Hlola i-Cell Collective kwi:
Landing.HeroDescription.HeroDescriptionL: Funda i-biology kunye ne-biochemistry ngokuzakhela nokwahlula.
Landing.SubHero.FeatureRichDescription: Isakhiwo soNxibelelwano, uhlalutyo kunye nokuboniswa konke, kwibhokisi enye.
Landing.ColumnBanner.BuildModelsDescript: Ukulinganisa ubuninzi beenkqubo ze-biological, kubandakanywa amanethiwekhi amaninzi, ulawulo lwemizi, ukuhanjiswa kwembonakaliso, amanxeba e-cell-interaction networks, i-webs zokutya, njl njl. Enxulumene nezinto ezihlukahlukeneyo ezivela kwiibhaktheriya ukuya kwiintsholongwane kwiintlanzi kwizityalo kubantu. Chaza imodeli ngaphandle kwesidingo sokungena okanye ukuguqula ukulingana kweemathematika eziyinkimbinkimbi.
Landing.ColumnBanner.PerformStimulations: Sebenzisa ixesha-langempela, ukulinganisa ngokubambisana ukubonakalisa ukuguqulwa kwenkqubo ye-biological phantsi kwe-extracellular eyahlukeneyo kunye nezimo zokuguquka (zezifo, izifo). Qalisa amakhulu emilinganiselo yokulinganisa kumcimbi wamaminithi kwaye wenze uhlalutyo lwengeniso-uphumela ukujonga iimpendulo zamaselula phantsi kweemeko ezahlukeneyo.
Landing.ColumnBanner.AnalyzeResultsDescr: Hlaziya i-dynamics kunye neempendulo zeenkqubo ze-biological phantsi kweemeko ezahlukeneyo. Ukuhlaziya ukuhlaziywa kwe-system-wide perturbation ukuqikelela nokubeka iziphumo zomntu ngamnye kunye nokudibanisa kwezinto kwiinkqubo. Yilungelelanise uphinde uphonononge amathuba okuvuselela iziyobisi kunye kunye namathuba okunxibelelana.
Landing.VideoBanner.VideoBannerDescripti: Abafundi abasasadingeki ukuba bazikhumbuze iingcinga zezinto eziphilayo - ziyakwenza umzekelo kwaye zilandelelanise ukusebenzisana okutshintshileyo kunokuba isebenzise isofthiwe ye-model Collective modeling.
Landing.VideoBanner.VideoBannerStudentMe: <em> Ndifumene ukuba ngokwenene ukwenza ezi ntlobo zemizekelo, ndiyayiqonda le migaqo emva koko. </ em>
Landing.VideoBanner.VideoBannerStudentTi: Umfundi weSayensi yezoBomi, <em> IYunivesithi yaseNebraska-Lincoln </ em>
LandingPage.UniversityBanner.UniversityB: Ama-1000 abaphandi, ootitshala nabafundi behlabathi lonke basebenzisa i-Cell Collective ukufunda, ukwakha nokwenza imizekelo yezinto eziphilayo.

Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase1.Publish:
• I-PUBLISHED IIMODELS zihlaziywe ngontanga, zipapashwe ziontanga zenziwe zifumaneke kwi-Community collective cell ukuze zifaniswe kunye negalelo elongezelelweyo.
  • IIMMODEL ZAMI ziqulethe iimodeli ezakhiwe kwaye ziphethwe nguwe.
  • UHLANGANE NAMANA yimizekelo abanye abasebenzisi abelana ngazo ngokuthe ngqo nawe. Sebenzisa le nto ukuze ukhethe ngqo kwaye uhlaziye imodeli kunye nabasebenzi bakho (ngaphandle kokuthumela iifayile ze-SBML zefayile emuva nangaphambili).
  • Skrolela ngasekunene ukubona amaModels angaphezulu!
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase1.YouMayC: Ungakchofoza uphawu {photo} nganoma naliphi ixesha ukuba ufunde malunga neenkalo ezininzi ze-Cell Collective.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ClickO: Cofa kwi icon ukutshintsha phakathi {photo1} (Indlela yokujonga) kunye {photo2} (Hlela indlela). <q> <li> Qhafaza kabini kwisithuba esingenanto ukwengeza icandelo elitsha. </ li> <li> Qhafaza kabini I-Label ukuze uqambe igama kwakhona. </ li> <li> Shift + iqhosha lokunene lokutshintsha phakathi phakathi okanye izinto zangaphandle. </ li> <li> Tshintshela phakathi kokusebenzisana okulungileyo okanye okungalunganga nguShift + ngokuchofoza ngakwesokunxele umgca wokuxhuma. </ li> </ ol>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.NewMod: Iinqununu ezintsha zeprojekthi zingaphinde zongezwe ngokuchofoza apha kwi {photo}. Chofoza kabini ilebula ukuhlela igama legama.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ToAddA: <span> Ukongeza i-activator okanye i-inhibitor, donsela uphinde ulahle izinto ezisuka kwiluhlu lwezinto zangaphakathi okanye ii-Components zangaphandle kwibhokisi yencoko yebhokisi yencoko. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ClickO: Cofa kwi {photo} icon ukugcina utshintsho lwakho.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.U: <span> Sebenzisa isilayidi esilula ukusekela iimeko zangaphandle (oko kukufakeliswa kweempawu). Amanqanaba angabuye ahluke ngexesha lokumlinganisa ukujonga ngenguqu kwiinguqu zenkqubo ngexesha langempela. Oku kufana nokutshintsha imeko yendalo kunye nokuqwalasela impendulo yayo. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.S: Khetha ibhokisi yokukhangela ngaphantsi kokubonakalayo {photo} icon yezinto oza kucinga ngazo kwiGrafu yokuLungisa. Ukunyuka phezu kwelebula yecandelo kuya kugxininisa indlela yayo, kukuvumela ukuba ufumane ngokukhawuleza icandelo ngaphakathi kwegrafu exakekile!
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.C: Cofa {photo1} icon ukuqala ukufaniswa. Unokukhafaza {photo2} ukumisa ukumemela nanini na okanye uphinde usethe ukulinganisa ngokuchofoza kwisithonjana {photo3}.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Cli: Cofa kwi {photo} icon ukudala uvavanyo olutsha. Iingcamango zithiwa ngokuthe ngqo ngokuchofoza kwilebula.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Use: <span> Sebenzisa isilayidi esilula ukuseta iimeko zangaphandle (oko kukubhaliweyo kokufaka). Oku kufana nokubeka iimpawu zangaphandle kwiinkqubo ze-biological ngaphakathi kwimo engqongileyo, ukuchaphazela impendulo yayo. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Cli: Click on  {photo} iicon to start the simulation.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Dos: <span> Iigrafu zempendulo ze-Dose zingenziwa nakweyiphi na into kwimodeli ngokukhetha icandelo elifanelekileyo kwi-X ne-Y-axis. Ngokuqhelekileyo, iqela langaphandle limelelwe kwi-X-axis (i-variable variable) kanti izakhi zangaphakathi zimelelwe kwi-Y axis (iimeko ezixhomekeke kuzo). Iimitha ezininzi zamaphetshana zempendulo zingenziwa kwizinto ezifanayo. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.YouMayS: <span> Unokukhangela imizekelo ngesihloko, inkcazo, iteks okanye igama leprotheni. Umbuzo owodwa uzakukhangela iimodeli ezishicilelweyo, iiModeli zam, kwaye zabiwe kunye nam ikhathalogu ngokukhawuleza. </ Span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.ChangeB: Shintsha phakathi koLuhlu kunye neGrid View
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.YouCanC: <span> Ungatshintsha umbono wakho phakathi kobuhlu bobubanzi kunye nombono wegridi. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.InThisM: <span> Kulo menyu ungahlela iphrofayili yakho yomsebenzisi, utshintshe iphasiwedi yakho, kwaye ungene ngemvume. </ span>
JoyDashboardRide.joyrideStepsModelPhase2: <span> Iimeko (okanye i-SubConditions) zisetyenziselwa ukubonakalisa ukuxhomekeka kokuxhasana okanye ukuxhomekeka kokuxhomekeka phakathi kwamanye amaqabane asebenzisanayo. Chofoza ukongeza ikhonkco ukuvula iPaneli yeemeko, udonsela uphinde ulawule amacandelo afanelekileyo (kwicandelo lokutsala) ibhokisi yencoko kwaye ucacise ukuba umqathango kufuneka usebenze okanye awusebenzi. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.ClickO: Iimodeli zichazwe kwaye zikhankanywe ngokusebenzisa iSiseko soLwazi. Cofa kwi {photo1} ukuze ungeze umxholo kunye {photo2} ukuze ungeze izikhombisi. Ngenisa nje i-IDM ye-PubMed Identifier (PMID) ukufomathiza ngokufomathiweyo kwaye udibanise amagama. Iingqinisiso zingabhalwa ngokubhekiselele kumpapasho kunye nohlobo lweedatha. Chofoza nje ngokuchanekileyo kwireferensi uze ukhethe ithegi ofuna ukuyongeza.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.Collab: Ukusebenzisana kubalulekile ekufumaneni ezintsha ngokusebenzisa indlela yokusebenza - kunye nentliziyo yeqoqo leqoqo! Ukuchofoza kwi {photo} kukuthatha kwiSahluko seSabelo, kukuvumela ukuba ungeze abambisene nabo, udale ii-link eziphathekayo kwaye ushicilele iimvavanyo.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.Select: <span> Khetha icandelo ofuna ukuguqula. Ukuqakraza ibhokisi ngokukhawuleza ukuguquka komsebenzi (kuboniswe ngumqondiso obomvu), kunye nokucofa ibhokisi ngokuphindwe kabini ukuguqulwa komsebenzi (kuboniswe ngongqakrazo oluhlaza). Ukuqakraza okwesithathu kuthintela utshintsho. Utshintshi lunokuqaliswa ngaphambi okanye ngexesha lokumilisela ukujonga ngenguqu kwiinguqu zengqondo ngexesha langempela. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase2.A: Yongeza u Rhu lumente wo kuqala
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase2.C: Cofa {photo} ukudala imeko yokuqala. Emva kokuba idala lokuqala lidalwe, i-icon iboniswa ngaphakathi kwepaneli yangaphakathi. Kule kholam, khetha iinqununu ofuna ukuzenzayo esebenzayo ekuqaleni kwesimangalo (t = 0).

Cofa {photo} ukurekhoda ukuhamba kweempawu. Ikhonkco iya kuphendulela oluhlaza emva kokurekhoda kuqhubeka. Utshintsho kwiimeko zokuzama okanye utshintsho, kunye nexesha elifanelekileyo lexesha lokuhamba, libhaliswe kwaye ligcinwe ngaphakathi kweempawu zokumemeza, okuvumela ukuphinda kuqhutywe kwamalinge asetshenziswe ngaphambili.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Mul: <span> Uvavanyo oluninzi lunokukhethwa ngokusebenzisa iibhokisi zokukhangela. Xa ukhe unyuliwe, unokususa, ukukopa okanye ukuqhuba kwakhona iimvavanyo ngexesha elinye. Oku kubaluleke kakhulu ukuhlaziya iimvavanyo emva kokwenza utshintsho kwindlela yokulawula imodeli. </ span>,
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Col: Cofa {photo} ecaleni kweNqabiso yoTyikityo: ilebula ukudala ukuhamba kweempawu. Ukuhlalutya ukulandelelana kweempawu akukwazi ukubhalwa, ngoko ke, iimeko zangaphandle (iimfuno) okanye utshintsho, kwaye uluhlu lwazo (i-time-point-occurrences) kufuneka zenziwe ngaphambili. Funda ukuhamba kweMigangatho yokuHlola ukuze uthole iinkcukacha ezingaphezulu.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Onc: <span> Emva kokuba unegrafu ekhutshwe apha ungayilanda iGraph Relations Activity njengefayile yePNG ngokuchofoza apha. </ span>
